    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111490/extras/b73b6f14d6a11e3592080e2c6bea68b3.avif?t=1668789591\" width=600 height=118 /></span><br>A setting from the 1st century A.D. is the cover letter of <strong>Sins From Magdala</strong> , in true <strong>escape room style</strong>, we are going to have to solve <strong>7 enigmas</strong> hidden in each corner of its rooms, each one related to a different deadly sin. Using as a basis the biblical verses in which it refers to the <strong>7 demons</strong> that <strong>Jesus expelled from Mary Magdalene</strong> :<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111490/extras/73fb33cb64f24428f019760d91b5ed45.avif?t=1668789591\" width=610 height=203 /></span><br><br>To solve them we must analyze each of the <strong>7 sins</strong> and make use of our<strong> virtues as human beings</strong> to correct what is wrong with us and know how to dominate the 7 demons that govern us, through different types of <strong>puzzles: visual, logical and of skill</strong> .<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2111490/extras/5c294028ea88e9ed5637518629933392.avif?t=1668789591\" width=610 height=202 /></span><br><br><strong>If you are a fan of puzzle games, come and live this adventure from a recondite place in the city of Magdala.</strong>",
